  "description": "A fixture is used to attach a Shape to a body for collision detection. A fixture\ninherits its transform from its parent. Fixtures hold additional non-geometric data\nsuch as friction, collision filters, etc.",
  "title": "Class Fixture",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture'>Class Fixture    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L43'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.html'>Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">A fixture is used to attach a Shape to a body for collision detection. A fixture\ninherits its transform from its parent. Fixtures hold additional non-geometric data\nsuch as friction, collision filters, etc.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public class Fixture</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Inheritance</h4><dl class=\"typelist inheritance\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.html'>Fixture</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Inherited Members</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object)'>object.Equals(object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object-system-object)'>object.Equals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gethashcode'>object.GetHashCode()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gettype'>object.GetType()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.memberwiseclone'>object.MemberwiseClone()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.referenceequals'>object.ReferenceEquals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.tostring'>object.ToString()</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Constructors</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.#ctor' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.#ctor' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture__ctor'>Fixture()    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L108'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Initializes a new instance of the <xref href=\"Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> class</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>internal Fixture()</code></pre><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.#ctor(Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.#ctor(Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape)' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture__ctor_Alis_Core_Physic_Collisions_Shapes_Shape_'>Fixture(Shape)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L123'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Initializes a new instance of the <xref href=\"Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> class</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public Fixture(Shape shape)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>shape</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.html'>Shape</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The shape</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Fields</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.AfterCollision' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.AfterCollision' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture_AfterCollision'>AfterCollision    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L63'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Fires after two shapes has collided and are solved. This gives you a chance to get the impact force.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public AfterCollisionEventHandler AfterCollision</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.AfterCollisionEventHandler.html'>AfterCollisionEventHandler</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.BeforeCollision' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.BeforeCollision' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture_BeforeCollision'>BeforeCollision    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L69'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Fires when two fixtures are close to each other.\nDue to how the broadphase works, this can be quite inaccurate as shapes are approximated using AABBs.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public BeforeCollisionEventHandler BeforeCollision</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.BeforeCollisionEventHandler.html'>BeforeCollisionEventHandler</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.CollidesWith' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.CollidesWith' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture_CollidesWith'>CollidesWith    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L74'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The collides with</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>internal Category CollidesWith</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Category.html'>Category</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.CollisionCategories' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.CollisionCategories' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture_CollisionCategories'>CollisionCategories    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L79'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The collision categories</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>internal Category CollisionCategories</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Category.html'>Category</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.CollisionGroup' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.CollisionGroup' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture_CollisionGroup'>CollisionGroup    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L84'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The collision group</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>internal short CollisionGroup</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.int16'>short</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.OnCollision' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.OnCollision' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture_OnCollision'>OnCollision    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L90'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Fires when two shapes collide and a contact is created between them.\nNote that the first fixture argument is always the fixture that the delegate is subscribed to.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public OnCollisionEventHandler OnCollision</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.OnCollisionEventHandler.html'>OnCollisionEventHandler</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.OnSeparation' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.OnSeparation' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture_OnSeparation'>OnSeparation    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L97'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Fires when two shapes separate and a contact is removed between them.\nNote: This can in some cases be called multiple times, as a fixture can have multiple contacts.\nNote The first fixture argument is always the fixture that the delegate is subscribed to.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public OnSeparationEventHandler OnSeparation</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.OnSeparationEventHandler.html'>OnSeparationEventHandler</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.Tag' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.Tag' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture_Tag'>Tag    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L103'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Set the user data. Use this to store your application specific data.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public object Tag</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture._friction' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture._friction' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture__friction'>_friction    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L48'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The friction</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>private float _friction</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.single'>float</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture._isSensor' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture._isSensor' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture__isSensor'>_isSensor    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L53'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The is sensor</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>private bool _isSensor</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.boolean'>bool</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture._restitution' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture._restitution' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture__restitution'>_restitution    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L58'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The restitution</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>private float _restitution</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.single'>float</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Properties</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.GetBody' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.GetBody' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture_GetBody'>GetBody    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L232'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Get the parent body of this fixture. This is null if the fixture is not attached.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public Body GetBody { get; internal set; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Body.html'>Body</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.GetCollidesWith' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.GetCollidesWith' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture_GetCollidesWith'>GetCollidesWith    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L168'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Defaults to Category.All\nThe collision mask bits. This states the categories that this\nfixture would accept for collision.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public Category GetCollidesWith { get; set; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Category.html'>Category</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.GetCollisionCategories' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.GetCollisionCategories' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture_GetCollisionCategories'>GetCollisionCategories    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L188'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The collision categories this fixture is a part of.\nDefaults to Category.Cat1</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public Category GetCollisionCategories { get; set; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Category.html'>Category</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.GetCollisionGroup' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.GetCollisionGroup' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture_GetCollisionGroup'>GetCollisionGroup    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L148'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Defaults to 0\nCollision groups allow a certain group of objects to never collide (negative)\nor always collide (positive). Zero means no collision group. Non-zero group\nfiltering always wins against the mask bits.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public short GetCollisionGroup { get; set; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.int16'>short</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.GetFriction' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.GetFriction' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture_GetFriction'>GetFriction    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L239'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Set the coefficient of friction. This will <em sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">not</em> change the friction of\nexisting contacts.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public float GetFriction { get; set; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.single'>float</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.GetIsSensor' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.GetIsSensor' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture_GetIsSensor'>GetIsSensor    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L214'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets or sets a value indicating whether this fixture is a sensor.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public bool GetIsSensor { get; set; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.boolean'>bool</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.GetRestitution' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.GetRestitution' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_Fixture_GetRestitution'>GetRestitution    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Dynamics/Fixture.cs#L250'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Set the coefficient of restitution. This will not change the restitution of\nexisting contacts.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public float GetRestitution { get; set; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.single'>float</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.GetShape' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.Fixture.GetShape' id='Alis_Core_Physi